data.description: This luxurious home features a first floor owner's suite, and is located within Spring House at Honey Farms ? a new townhome community located just 3.5 miles from Saturn Parkway. The largest of the townhome offerings in Spring House at Honey Farms, the Wisteria has been carefully crafted to let you indulge while enjoying unsurpassed comfort, quality and practicality in a townhome. Step inside the two-story foyer, you'll be drawn to the wide open kitchen and great room that lie ahead. High above, a fabulous vaulted ceiling caps off the area. The gourmet kitchen features an oversized island, stainless appliances, granite countertops and premium vinyl plank flooring.. Adjacent to the kitchen is a powder room, first-floor laundry and access to the large two-car garage. The luxurious owner's bedroom is tucked away off the great room and features a private bath and large walk-in closet. From the entryway, stairs ascend to the large second floor loft with stunning view of the great room below. Two roomy upstairs bedrooms share an adjoining Jack-and-Jill bath. Storage abounds in the Wisteria with large walk-in closets in each bedroom, a deep closet in the foyer, plus a pantry-style closet just off the kitchen. Unlike traditional townhome designs, the Wisteria provides the distinct advantages of a luxurious, well-appointed home. See for yourself just how sweet life can be in this distinctive home in Spring House at Honey Farms. Contact us today to set up a tour!
